<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5241639>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20–27. Picobia corcoracus sp. nov. (female). 20, gnathosoma in dorsal view; 21, propodosoma in ventral view; 22, seta ve; 23, Propodosoma in dorsal view; 24, opisthosoma in ventral view; 25, opisthosoma in dorsal view; 26, opisthosomal lobe; 27, tarsus III. Scale lines 100 µm (Fig. 25); 75 µm (Figs. 21, 23, 24); 50 µm (Figs. 20, 26), 20µm (Figs. 22, 27)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5241639/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

